XC_NATURE BY CHICHIN

This is my first climb map. I know its short and not very hard map. Try to be the fastest climber. My own record is 3:05. I think you can be better ^^ I added 2 bonuses: Maze is left port and bhop is right port. Try it. Thanks to Mr.SkalPel for his advanced timer tutorial. Good Luck & Have Fun ^^
